{"tid":145571,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"失業真係好Q正","createTime":"2017-03-06T11:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T13:14:50.000Z","uid":55851,"like":327,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"55b3ff0cd6b35b1ae59009695f96f9f350436b28","tid":145571,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多,&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右,&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"a716d2bfb703e362a981129d7e2dacc598835760","tid":145571,"uid":88544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:02:26.000Z","msg":"願你開工"},{"pid":"0c71b0bb56ade3987c45fa6db18e36d936b975ca","tid":145571,"uid":2566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ccb805fb11103d8012b493187fa779e5ad1a40","tid":145571,"uid":58046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385b34e230ee29deaeb47e871d7903f15a2c4dee","tid":145571,"uid":75287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:13:09.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eba5ae52d27a1e5dadd6baa2d10fb97420b1100","tid":145571,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"c5bc608f22d53f57f52dac81fcbbc2dd7ab292f7","tid":145571,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:14:20.000Z","m